    "Previous exam papers (as used in this case study) are important in this formative assessment process, and these include exam questions that have previously been used in the same medical exam and are available to medical students who wish to practice for upcoming exams.",
    "Feed up in this case study is thus related to the medicine exam set that consisted of 110 exam questions in Norwegian language (MD4062) from 2020.",
    "Feedback is a critical component of formative assessment, providing students with information regarding their current performance relative to the learning goals.",
    "Effective feedback and formative assessments help students identify their strengths and areas for improvement, ultimately enhancing their understanding and performance.",
    "In this study, GPT-4's ability to generate feedback on the summative assessment (feed up) attached to the first research question was evaluated using 110 exam questions and 10 blinded exam questions."
